GIMP JPEG-2000 plugin
=====================

To build and install it :

1. Ensure you have installed required dependancies, then build using :

	./configure
	make
	make install



Dependancies
============

1. GIMP SDK from 2.10.20  (on Windows, it seems you need to build GIMP from source to get this - linux you can install libgimp2.0-dev)
2. OpenJPEG 2.3.1



Install
=======

Linux: make  install above should install the plugin for you.

Windows : If you want to run with standard Desktop installed GIMP version, rather than the version you just build using msys2, copy jp2.exe from src directory to

C:\Users\[User]\AppData\Roaming\GIMP\2.10\plug-ins